.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-LOCAL-PCT-RANGE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-local-pct-range \- FEAT-2788 peer-local-pct-range
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-local-pct-range
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the range (max minus min) of local balance percentage across peers (FEAT-2788).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBlocal_pct_range\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
